"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447207","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-02-01","<p>We expect the Successor submarine programme will sustain thousands of jobs at Barrow into the 2030s. These jobs will ensure that the UK retains and develops its world leading skills at Barrow and a wide range of companies across the nation, making a significant contribution to the UK economy.</p>","Ludlow","Mr Philip Dunne",,"2016-02-01T17:36:38.523Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447207/answer","Biography information for Mr Philip Dunne","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447207/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447207/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-01-25","Trident Submarines: Job Creation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what recent estimate his Department has made of the number of jobs which  will be created at Barrow shipyards by the Successor submarine project; and what estimate it has made of the anticipated duration of employment of those jobs.","false","Biography information for Margaret Ferrier","Rutherglen and Hamilton West","Margaret Ferrier","23982"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447208","Cabinet Office","false","2016-01-28","<p>Senior members of the National Security Council meet frequently to discuss matters of national security but we do not disclose information about the detail of these internal proceedings and discussions.</p>","West Dorset","Mr Oliver Letwin",,"2016-01-28T14:25:45.74Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447208/answer","Biography information for Sir Oliver Letwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447208/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447208/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2016-01-25","National Security Council: Meetings","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, pursuant to the Answer of 16 September 2015 to Question 9748, on counter-terrorism, on what date the meeting of the most senior members of the National Security Council referred to in that Answer took place.","false","Biography information for Mr David Davis","Haltemprice and Howden","Mr David Davis","23904"
